ed="T" n="0807a23"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0807a23"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000018831"><placeName>江州</placeName><placeName>興果寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A011324">神湊</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0807a24"/><persName key="A011324">釋神湊</persName>，姓<name>成</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000042576"><placeName>京兆</placeName><placeName>藍田</placeName></placeName>人也。生而奇秀，丱<lb
ed="T" n="0807a25"/>角出塵，遠慕戒律，祈<placeName key="PL000000028928">南嶽</placeName><persName key="A010470">希操<roleName>師</roleName></persName>受具，復<lb
ed="T" n="0807a26"/>參<placeName key="PL000000018628">鐘陵</placeName><persName key="A003623">大寂<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>。然則志在《楞嚴經》<ptr target="#n92"/>，行在<lb
ed="T" n="0807a27"/>《四分律》<ptr target="#n70"/>，其他諸教，餘力則通。<date from-iso="+0773-02-01" key="j20034242003806" to-iso="+0774-02-18"><name>大曆</name>八年</date>，制懸<lb
ed="T" n="0807a28"/>經、論、律三科策試天下出家者，中等第方<lb
ed="T" n="0807a29"/>度。<persName key="A011324">湊</persName>應是選，詔配<placeName key="PL000000018831"><placeName>九江</placeName><placeName>興果精舍</placeName></placeName>。後從僧<pb ed="T" n="0807b" xml:id="T50.2061.0807b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0807b01"/>望移居<placeName key="PL000000018801">東林寺</placeName>，即<placeName key="PL000000005488">雁門</placeName><persName key="A001204">賈遠</persName>之舊道場也，<lb
ed="T" n="0807b02"/>有<placeName key="PL000000018804">甘露戒壇</placeName>、<placeName>白蓮池</placeName>在焉。既居是，嗣興佛<lb
ed="T" n="0807b03"/>事，雖經論資神，終研律成務。<persName key="A011324">湊</persName>羸瘠，視之<lb
ed="T" n="0807b04"/>頹然，州將門人醫療，而不願進藥。<date from-iso="+0817-10-18" key="j20197542019783" to-iso="+0817-11-16"><name>元和</name>十<lb
ed="T" n="0807b05"/>二年九月</date>遘疾<ptr target="#n1490"/>，<date key="j20197792019779" when-iso="+0817-11-12">二十六日</date>儼然坐終于<placeName key="PL000000018801">寺</placeName>。<date key="j20198022019802" when-iso="+0817-12-05">十<lb
ed="T" n="0807b06"/>月十九日</date>，門人奉全身窆于寺西道北，祔<lb
ed="T" n="0807b07"/><persName key="A001204">雁門</persName>墳左──若<persName key="A002231">僧詮</persName>葬近<persName key="A002883">郭文</persName>之墓也。春秋<lb
ed="T" n="0807b08"/>七十四，夏臘五十一。<persName key="A011324">湊</persName>以精進心脂不退<lb
ed="T" n="0807b09"/>輪，以勇健力撾無畏鼓，故登壇秉法垂三<lb
ed="T" n="0807b10"/>十年，一盂而食，一榻而居<ptr target="#n1847"/>，衣縫枲麻<ptr type="glossary" target="#g760"/>，坐薦<lb
ed="T" n="0807b11"/>藁秸<ptr type="glossary" target="#g764"/>。由茲檀施<ptr type="glossary" target="#g237"/>臻集于躬，即迴入常住<ptr type="glossary" target="#g151"/>無<lb
ed="T" n="0807b12"/>盡財<ptr type="glossary" target="#g645"/>中，與眾共之。每夜捧鑪秉燭，行道<anchor xml:id="beg0807sgsz5"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0807sgsz5"/><lb
ed="T" n="0807b13"/>佛，徇<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g1275"/>十二時，少有廢闕，如是經四十五<lb
ed="T" n="0807b14"/>載<ptr target="#n1848"/>。生常遇<persName key="A004029">白樂天</persName>為典午<ptr type="glossary" target="#g771"/>于郡，相善。及終，<lb
ed="T" n="0807b15"/>悲悼，作《塔銘》云：「本結菩提香火社，共嫌煩<lb
ed="T" n="0807b16"/>惱電泡身<ptr target="#n1849"/>，不須惆悵隨<ptr target="#n484"/>師去，先請西方作<lb
ed="T" n="0807b17"/>主人。」</p>
